Hey, Kimmi, come here, will ya?
Got you something.

38:54.542 --> 38:57.667
- Oh, Uncle Kris.
I didn't really get you anything.

38:58.208 --> 38:59.250
- Merry Christmas.

39:00.000 --> 39:02.833
I had it taped to the wall of my cell
right next to my bed,

39:03.333 --> 39:07.208
and, um, I was remembering
when your dad passed away

39:07.208 --> 39:08.833
how hard it was on the family.

39:09.333 --> 39:10.625
And how your mom,

39:10.625 --> 39:12.875
you know, she just
kind of threw herself into her work

39:12.875 --> 39:16.000
